Package leeLogger

Class BinaryOperations

java.lang.Object
leeLogger.BinaryOperations
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class BinaryOperations
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Class saves binary data and reads binary data from a .BIN file The BinaryOperations class takes in the transactions as a list Object and saves the data to directory "Resources/UserData.Bin". The same file is used for storage and is read when the user re-starts the application.
Author:
leefowler
